data.description: Come home to quiet on the cul-de-sac.  This 4 bed 2.5 bath home has been used multiple ways.  The current, expansive master bedroom has historically been used as a family room and also as a daycare.  It has it's own separate, front exterior access so new owner could use creatively as well.  The private backyard is your own little sanctuary.  Come check it out, you may just want to stay for a very long time!
